ğŸ“Œ 2. Process in CrewAI

Process defines **how tasks are executed**.

CrewAI supports two major processes:

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ”¹ 2.1 Sequential Process

Tasks run in fixed order.

```text
Task 1 â†’ Task 2 â†’ Task 3 â†’ Final Output
```

Best for:

* Report generation
* Structured workflows

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ”¹ 2.2 Hierarchical Process

A manager (planner) assigns tasks dynamically.

```text
Manager Agent
   â†“
Assigns tasks
   â†“
Worker Agents execute
   â†“
Manager reviews
```

Best for:

* Complex workflows
* Dynamic decision-making
* Multi-step planning

